{"lemma":"ظُلْمُ","slug":"ظُلْمُ","root":"ظ.ل.م","root_slug":"ظ-ل-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ظ-ل-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"ظُلْم","root":"ظلم","pos":"N","occurrence_count":20},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":6,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n27637","n27642","n27643","n27645","n27646"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B8%D9%8F%D9%84%D9%92%D9%85%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to wrong, to treat unjustly, to oppress","examples":[{"text":"إِنَّمَا السَّبِيلُ عَلَى الَّذِينَ يَظْلِمُونَ النَّاسَ وَيَبْغُونَ فِي الْأَرْضِ بِغَيْرِ الْحَقِّ ۚ أُولَٰئِكَ لَهُمْ عَذَابٌ أَلِيمٌ","english":"Indeed, the blame lieth only upon those ones who oppress [their fellow] Man, and who are insolent throughout the earth without any right whatsoever. They are those for whom a punishment most painful [will suffice]."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to become dark"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be in the least unjust"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of ظَلَمَ (ẓalama) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"wrong, wrongdoing, injustice, injuriousness, tyranny"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of ظَلَمَ (ẓalama) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of ظُلْمَة (ẓulma)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare Aramaic טלם.\n\nSee ظَلَام (ẓalām)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n27637","headword_ar":"ظَلَمَ","root":"Zlm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", has for its inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalomN","text_ar":"ظَلْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, Msb, K, and so in some copies of the S,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulomN","text_ar":"ظُلْمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (so in other copies of the S,) or both, (T,) or the latter is a simple subst., (T, M, Msb, TA,) which is put in the place of the inf. n., (TA, [and the same is indicated in the T and K by the saying that the proper inf. n. is with fet-h,]) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maZolimapN","text_ar":"مَظْلِمَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) or this is likewise a simple subst., (Msb,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maZolamapN","text_ar":"مَظْلَمَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [or this also is a simple subst.,] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZilaAmN","text_ar":"ظِلَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"also is said to be an inf. n. like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulomN","text_ar":"ظُلْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", these two being like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"libaAsN","text_ar":"لِبَاسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lubosN","text_ar":"لُبْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [or it is a simple subst. like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulomN","text_ar":"ظُلْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said to be, or it is an inf. n. of 3, as such occurring in the middle of this paragraph,] or, accord. to Kr, it is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulomN","text_ar":"ظُلْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rimaAHN","text_ar":"رِمَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rumoHN","text_ar":"رُمْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalama","text_ar":"ظَلَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"when intrans. generally means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did wrong;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acted wrongfully, unjustly, injuriously,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tyrannically:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and when trans.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he wronged;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"treated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"used, wrongfully, unjustly, injuriously,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tyrannically;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he misused:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] accord. to most of the lexicologists, (Er-Rághib, TA,) primarily, (As, T, S, Msb,) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlZ~ulomu","text_ar":"الظُّلْمُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the putting a thing in a place not its own; putting it in a wrong place; misplacing it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, T, S, M, Er-Rághib, Msb, K:) and it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by exceeding"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by falling short,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by deviating from the proper time and place:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the acting in whatsoever way one pleases in the disposal of the property of another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the transgressing the proper limit:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(El-Munáwee, TA:) [i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the transgressing the proper limit much"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"little:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA:) or, accord. to some, it primarily signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aqoS","text_ar":"النَّقْص"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the making to suffer loss,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"detriment"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (MF, TA:) and it is said to be of three kinds,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between man and God,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between man and man,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between a man and himself;"},{"kind":"text","text":"every one of which three is really"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liln~afosi","text_ar":"لِلنَّفْسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a wrongdoing to oneself"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Er-Rághib, TA:) [when it is used as a simple subst.,] the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulomN","text_ar":"ظُلْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to Kr. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZilaAmN","text_ar":"ظِلَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as mentioned above, and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulaAmN","text_ar":"ظُلَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with damm, is said to be syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulomN","text_ar":"ظُلْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or a pl. thereof, [of an extr. form, commonly regarded as that of a quasi-pl. n.,] like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruxaAlN","text_ar":"رُخَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mani A@sotaroEaY Al*~iy^oba faqado Zalama","text_ar":"مَنِ ا@سْتَرْعَى الذِّيْبَ فَقَدْ ظَلَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He who asks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desires, the wolf to keep guard surely does wrong,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"puts a thing in a wrong place"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: a prov. (S, Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mano A^a$obaha A^abaAhu famaA Zalama","text_ar":"مَنْ اَشْبَهَ اَبَاهُ فَمَا ظَلَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (As, T, S,) a prov., meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Whoso resembles his father"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a quality, or an attribute,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he has not put the likeness in a wrong place."},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, T. [See art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$bh","text_ar":"شبه"},{"kind":"text","text":".])"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"walamo","text_ar":"وَلَمْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taZolimo minohu $ayoy^FA","text_ar":"تَظْلِمْ مِنْهُ شَيْيًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [xviii. 31], means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"walamo tanoquSo","text_ar":"وَلَمْ تَنْقُصْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And made not aught thereof to suffer loss,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"detriment"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (M, K:) and in like manner Fr explains the saying in the Kur [ii. 54 and vii. 160],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wamaA ZalamuwnaA wal`kino kaAnuwA A^anofusahumo","text_ar":"وَمَا ظَلَمُونَا وَلٰكِنْ كَانُوا اَنْفُسَهُمْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaZolimuwna","text_ar":"يَظْلِمُونَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And they made not us to suffer loss,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"detriment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"by that which they did,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but themselves they made to suffer loss,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"detriment:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA:) in which sense it seems to be indicated in the A that the verb is tropical. (TA.) ―         -b2-  It is also trans. by means of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bi","text_ar":"بِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as in the phrase in the Kur [vii. 101 and xvii. 61]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faZalamuwA bihaA","text_ar":"فَظَلَمُوا بِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", because the meaning is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kafaruwA","text_ar":"كَفَرُوا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And they disbelieved in them"},{"kind":"text","text":"], referring to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=yaAt","text_ar":"ا=يَات"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"signs"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (M, TA; *) the verb having this meaning tropically or by implication; or being thus made trans. because implying the meaning of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~ako*iyb","text_ar":"التَّكْذِيب"},{"kind":"text","text":": or [the meaning is, and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they wronged"},{"kind":"text","text":"themselves, or the people,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"because of them;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for], as some say, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"b","text_ar":"ب"},{"kind":"text","text":"is causative, and the objective complement, i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anofusahumo","text_ar":"اَنْفُسَهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aAsa","text_ar":"النَّاسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", is suppressed. (TA.) ―         -b3-  And it is doubly trans. by itself: (TA:) one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalamahu Haq~ahu","text_ar":"ظَلَمَهُ حَقَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made him to suffer loss,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"detriment, of his right,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"due;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"defrauded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"despoiled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deprived, him of it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haq~ahu","text_ar":"حَقَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tZl~mhu","text_ar":"تظلّمهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) [and] you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taZal~amaniY","text_ar":"تَظَلَّمَنِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [as well as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tZl~mnY maAliY","text_ar":"تظلّمنى مَالِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", occurring in a verse cited in the M,] meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalamaniY maAliY","text_ar":"ظَلَمَنِى مَالِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one caused me to suffer loss,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of my property"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) It is said in the Kur [iv. 44],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a A@ll~`ha laA","text_ar":"اـِنَّ ا@للّٰهَ لَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaZolimu mivoqaAla *ar~apK","text_ar":"يَظْلِمُ مِثْقَالَ ذَرَّةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA yaZolimuhumo mivoqaAla *ar~api","text_ar":"لَا يَظْلِمُهُمْ مِثْقَالَ ذَرَّةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the verb is made doubly trans. because the meaning is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA yasolubuhumo","text_ar":"لَا يَسْلُبُهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily God will not despoil them,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deprive them, of the weight of one of the smallest of ants,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a grub of an ant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mivoqaAla *ar~apK","text_ar":"مِثْقَالَ ذَرَّةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", may be put in the place of the inf. n., for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalomFA HaqiyrFA kamivoqaAli *ar~apK","text_ar":"ظَلْمًا حَقِيرًا كَمِثْقَالِ ذَرَّةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with a paltry spoliation"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deprivation, such as the weight of one of the smallest of ants,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (M.) ―         -b4-  One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^araAda ZilaAmahu","text_ar":"اَرَادَ ظِلَامَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muZaAlamatahu","text_ar":"مُظَالَمَتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [these two nouns being inf. ns. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZaAlamahu","text_ar":"ظَالَمَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", or the former, as mentioned above, is, accord. to some, an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalama","text_ar":"ظَلَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zulomahu","text_ar":"ظُلْمَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalomahu","text_ar":"ظَلْمَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He desired the wronging,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M, K.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalamahu","text_ar":"ظَلَمَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulomN","text_ar":"ظُلْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalomN","text_ar":"ظَلْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"?], also means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He imposed upon him a thing that was above his power,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuZolamu","text_ar":"يُظْلَمُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is asked for a thing that is above his power,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b6-  And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalama AlbaEiyra","text_ar":"ظَلَمَ البَعِيرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He slaughtered the camel without disease."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zulimati Aln~aAqapu","text_ar":"ظُلِمَتِ النَّاقَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The she-camel was slaughtered without disease:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was covered without her desiring the stallion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalama AlHimaAru AlA^ataAna","text_ar":"ظَلَمَ الحِمَارُ الاَتَانَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The he-ass leaped the she-ass"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"before her time:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when she was pregnant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) so in the A. (TA.) ―         -b7-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalama AlwaToba","text_ar":"ظَلَمَ الوَطْبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulomN","text_ar":"ظُلْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalomN","text_ar":"ظَلْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"?], (S,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave to drink of the milk of his skin before its becoming thick"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and its butter's coming forth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA. [And the like is said in the T and M.]) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalama Alqawoma","text_ar":"ظَلَمَ القَوْمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave to drink to the people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"milk before it had attained to maturity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, K,) as related on the authority of A 'Obeyd, (T,) or ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"milk such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zaliymap","text_ar":"ظَلِيمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M:) but this is a mistake: it is related on the authority of Ahmad Ibn-Yahyà [i. e. Th] and AHeyth that one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalamotu Als~iqaA='a","text_ar":"ظَلَمْتُ السِّقَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"All~abana","text_ar":"اللَّبَنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I drank,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gave to drink, what was in the skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the milk, before its attaining to maturity and the extracting of its butter:"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to ISk, one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalamotu waTobiYa Alqawoma","text_ar":"ظَلَمْتُ وَطْبِىَ القَوْمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [but I think that it is correctly"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalamotu waTobiY liloqawmi","text_ar":"ظَلَمْتُ وَطْبِى لِلْقَومِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", agreeably with a verse cited in the T and M,] meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I gave to drink"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the contents of my milk-skin before the thickening thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalamotuhu","text_ar":"ظَلَمْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said of anything as meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I did it hastily,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hurriedly, before its proper time,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"season."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalamotu AlHawoDa","text_ar":"ظَلَمْتُ الحَوْضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I made the watering-trough in a place in which watering-troughs should not be made."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, T.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalama AlA^aroDa","text_ar":"ظَلَمَ الاَرْضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He dug the ground in what was not the place of digging:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when it had not been dug before."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) And, said of a torrent, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It furrowed the earth in a place that was not furrowed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalama","text_ar":"ظَلَمَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbiTaAHa","text_ar":"البِطَاحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a torrent, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It reached the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bTAH","text_ar":"بطاح"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wide water-courses containing fine,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"broken, pebbles,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not having reached them before."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalama AlwaAdiY","text_ar":"ظَلَمَ الوَادِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The water of the valley reached a place that it had not reached before."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, T, S, K, TA.) ―         -b9-  When men have added upon the grave other than its own earth,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA taZolimuwA","text_ar":"لَا تَظْلِمُوا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Transgress not ye the proper limit"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is said to them. (TA.) ―         -b10-  And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA","text_ar":"لَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taZolimo waDaHa AlT~ariyqi","text_ar":"تَظْلِمْ وَضَحَ الطَّرِيقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Turn not thou from the main part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the beaten track, of the road."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA taZolimo Eanohu $ayoy^aA","text_ar":"لَا تَظْلِمْ عَنْهُ شَيْيَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Turn not thou from it at all."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lazima AlT~ariyqa falamo yaZolimohu","text_ar":"لَزِمَ الطَّرِيقَ فَلَمْ يَظْلِمْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He kept to the road, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"did not turn from it to the right and left."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b11-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA Zalamaka","text_ar":"مَا ظَلَمَكَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ano tafoEala","text_ar":"اَنْ تَفْعَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, K, TA) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What has prevented thy doing"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA) such a thing? (TA.) A man complained to Abu-l-Jarráh of his suffering indigestion from food that he had eaten, and he said to him,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA Zalamaka A^ano taqiYo'a","text_ar":"مَا ظَلَمَكَ اَنْ تَقِىْءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What has prevented thy vomiting?"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Fr, T.) And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA Zalamaka Eano ka*aA","text_ar":"مَا ظَلَمَكَ عَنْ كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What has prevented thee from such a thing?"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.) Respecting the saying"},{"kind":"quote","text":"qaAla balaY yaA maY~a waAlyawomu Zalamo"},{"kind":"text","text":"[addressed by a man to a woman who had invited him to visit her], Fr says, they say that the meaning is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haq~FA","text_ar":"حَقًّا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Truly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in truth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He said, Yes, O Meiya, truly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in truth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"I will visit thee]; and it is a prov.; (T;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alyawomu Zalama","text_ar":"اليَوْمُ ظَلَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaY waAlyawomu Zalama","text_ar":"بَلَى وَاليَوْمُ ظَلَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", is a prov.; (Meyd;) and thus it was expl. by IAar, as used in the manner of an oath: but Fr says, in my opinion the meaning is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and a day in which is a cause of prevention shall not prevent me:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[so that the words of the hemistich above may be rendered,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he said, Yes, O Meiya, though the day present an obstacle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"for I will overcome every obstacle]: (T:)"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1921},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to Kr,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadima fulaAnN waAlyawomu Zalama","text_ar":"قَدِمَ فُلَانٌ وَاليَوْمُ ظَلَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one came truly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in truth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or it may be rendered"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such a one came though the day presented an obstacle:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] but in the saying"},{"kind":"quote","text":"A_in~a AlfiraAqa Alyawoma waAlyawomu Zalamo"},{"kind":"text","text":"the meaning is said by some to be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAlyawomu ZalamanaA","text_ar":"وَاليَوْمُ ظَلَمَنَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily separation is to-day, and the day has wronged"},{"kind":"text","text":"(us)]: or, as some say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zlm","text_ar":"ظلم"},{"kind":"text","text":"here means,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"has put the thing in a wrong place:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) accord. to ISk, the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAlyawomu Zalam","text_ar":"وَاليَوْمُ ظَلَم"},{"kind":"text","text":"means ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"though,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the day has put the affair in a wrong place."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.) [See also Freytag's Arab. Prov. ii. 911.]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalima","text_ar":"ظَلِمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of the night: see 4."}],"source_refs":["T","M","Msb","TA","S","As","MF","K"]},{"entry_id":"n27642","headword_ar":"ظَلْمٌ","root":"Zlm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lustre,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"brightness, of gold."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Z, TA.) ―         -b2-  And hence, (Z, TA,) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lustre"},{"kind":"text","text":"(lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"running water"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon the teeth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T, Z, TA;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lustre"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA='","text_ar":"مَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":", S, M, K, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariyq","text_ar":"بَرِيق"},{"kind":"text","text":", S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the teeth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T, S, M, Z, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the clearness of the colour, not from the saliva,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, * T, * M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like blackness within the bone thereof, by reason of the intense whiteness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resembling the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"firinod","text_ar":"فِرِنْد"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the sword,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appearing like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"firinod","text_ar":"فِرِنْد"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the sword"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that one imagines that there is in it a blackness, by reason of the intense lustre and clearness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) or, accord. to Sh,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whiteness of the teeth, as though there were upon it"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"somewhat of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a blackness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as Abu-l-'Abbás ElAhwal says, in the Expos. of the “ Kaabeeyeh, ”"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lustre"},{"kind":"text","text":"(lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"running water"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the teeth, such that one sees upon it, by reason of its intense clearness"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"transparency"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what resembles dustcolour and blackness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, accord. to another explanation,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fineness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thinness, and intense whiteness, of the teeth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZuluwmN","text_ar":"ظُلُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, M.) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Snow:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) it is said to have this meaning: and the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mu$orabapi Alv~anaAyaA bimaA='i AlZ~alomi","text_ar":"مُشْرَبَةِ الثَّنَايَا بِمَا=ءِ الظَّلْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", used by a poet, may mean ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Having the central teeth suffused with the lustre termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalom","text_ar":"ظَلْم"},{"kind":"text","text":", as is indicated in the T and S, or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the water of snow."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T.)"}],"source_refs":["Z","TA","Lth","T","S","M","K"]},{"entry_id":"n27643","headword_ar":"ظُلْمٌ","root":"Zlm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[as a simple subst. generally means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Wrong, wrongdoing, injustice, injuriousness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tyranny"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: see 1, first sentence, in two places. ―         -b2-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zulomu","text_ar":"ظُلْمُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlArDi","text_ar":"الارضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the CK is a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalama","text_ar":"ظَلَمَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^aroDa","text_ar":"الاَرْضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlZulomu","text_ar":"الظُلْمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in one place in the CK, as syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlZ~alomaA='u","text_ar":"الظَّلْمَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", is a mistake for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlZ~ulomapu","text_ar":"الظُّلْمَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n27645","headword_ar":"ظُلَمٌ","root":"Zlm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an appellation of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Three nights"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the lunar month"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"next after the three called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duraEN","text_ar":"دُرَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T, S, * K; *) so says A'Obeyd: (T:) thus called because of their darkness: (S:) the sing. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalomaA='u","text_ar":"ظَلْمَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T, S;) so that it is anomalous; for by rule it should be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulomN","text_ar":"ظُلْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) and the sing. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duraEN","text_ar":"دُرَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daroEaA='u","text_ar":"دَرْعَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": so says A'Obeyd: but accord. to AHeyth and Mbr, the sings. are ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulomapN","text_ar":"ظُلْمَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1922},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duroEapN","text_ar":"دُرْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", agreeably with rule; and this is the correct assertion. (T. [See more in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"drE","text_ar":"درع"},{"kind":"text","text":", voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adoraEu","text_ar":"اَدْرَعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".])"}],"source_refs":["T","S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n27646","headword_ar":"ظِلَمٌ","root":"Zlm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zil~aAmN","text_ar":"ظِلَّامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}